00:00:00.992 --> 00:00:04.079
Today, we are here to celebrate the birthday of Shri Jesus Christ.

00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:08.190
Jesus Christ's life was very short and He spent most of His time in India, in Kashmir.

00:00:08.391 --> 00:00:11.907
He went back just for last three years

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:15.720
and people fixed Him to a cross.

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:26.560
It was somewhat destined.

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:32.400
To open Agnya chakra

00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:34.560
He had to offer this sacrifice.

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:37.880
So in this way He

00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:42.000
set up Agnya chakra.

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:45.960
Agnya chakra is very

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.400
constricted

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:52.360
small

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.200
and not easily openable,

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.560
because a human being

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:03.400
got freedom

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.920
that made him egoistic.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:10.680
This ego

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:13.880
constricted his Agnya chakra.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.199
And from that

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:22.253
constricted Agnya chakra

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:25.182
it was necessary to take out ego.

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:29.400
And to take out ego

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:33.960
you have to control your (MAAN).

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.360
But you do not take out your ego from your (MAAN).

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:44.400
As soon as you will try to take out your ego from your (MAAN)

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:50.160
the (MAAN) will go on increasing

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:52.600
and the ego will go on increasing

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:55.600
[ AHAAM  KAROTI  SAHA  AHAMKAR ]

00:01:56.680 --> 00:01:57.800
We do !

