You may do anything

00:48:59.520 --> 00:49:02.200
You are not connected. Your connection is missing.

00:49:03.440 --> 00:49:05.760
Christ is missing. He is no more.

00:49:08.160 --> 00:49:13.040
To establish Him first of all you must show how you love.

00:49:13.360 --> 00:49:15.880
That doesn't mean that you love your wife,

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:18.360
love your children and love your house.

00:49:20.000 --> 00:49:22.120
You have to love everyone.

00:49:23.560 --> 00:49:26.280
Try to make everyone happy.

00:49:27.480 --> 00:49:28.880
That is why I like music

00:49:29.000 --> 00:49:32.120
because through music you can spread vibrations.

00:49:33.360 --> 00:49:36.280
Very good media of spreading vibrations

00:49:37.280 --> 00:49:39.039
of loving vibrations.

00:49:39.240 --> 00:49:43.320
But those who are musicians have to be loving people,

00:49:45.320 --> 00:49:46.637
not hot tempered

00:49:48.240 --> 00:49:49.645
not showing off

00:49:51.400 --> 00:49:54.160
not thinking too much of themselves.

00:49:55.600 --> 00:49:57.000
All these will work

00:49:57.760 --> 00:49:59.800
very well if you understand

00:50:00.000 --> 00:50:03.000
that this Divine power

00:50:03.200 --> 00:50:05.120
is so powerful.

00:50:07.080 --> 00:50:08.200
No doubt it is love,

00:50:09.000 --> 00:50:11.400
no doubt it is truth,

00:50:12.320 --> 00:50:14.000
and no doubt

00:50:15.680 --> 00:50:19.600
if you get out of it, you will be caught up by anything

00:50:19.800 --> 00:50:21.800
and you could be finished.

00:50:24.120 --> 00:50:26.400
It is a very very

00:50:27.600 --> 00:50:32.680
powerful, effective and absolutely conclusive

00:50:33.840 --> 00:50:36.160
power you have within yourself.

00:50:37.280 --> 00:50:40.080
And thanks to christ that crucified Himself

00:50:40.440 --> 00:50:42.840
sacrificed his body for our sake

00:50:43.120 --> 00:50:44.600
that our agnya is opened up.

00:50:44.800 --> 00:50:47.200
Otherwise I could not have done this Sahajyoga.

00:50:49.520 --> 00:50:51.160
But in this area

00:50:51.360 --> 00:50:54.600
we have Buddha, Christ and Mahavira.

00:50:57.040 --> 00:50:59.640
and they had to do tapasya, tapaha.

00:51:00.120 --> 00:51:01.040
They did it.

00:51:01.240 --> 00:51:04.800
You don't have to do now, they have done for you.

00:51:09.560 --> 00:51:12.000
Now see I saw the musicians yesterday.

00:51:12.200 --> 00:51:14.599
In two three months they have learnt so much,

00:51:14.800 --> 00:51:17.800
otherwise formerly  all the musicians I knew.

00:51:18.000 --> 00:51:19.360
For Indian music

00:51:20.240 --> 00:51:21.960
had to really starve.

00:51:22.560 --> 00:51:24.800
For months together they had to practice

00:51:25.000 --> 00:51:28.720
years together, they had to bow to their guru.

00:51:28.920 --> 00:51:30.880
That is all over now.

00:51:33.320 --> 00:51:35.480
because of this Param Chaitanya

00:51:35.680 --> 00:51:37.480
and your power

00:51:38.720 --> 00:51:41.080
to be one with the Divine.

00:51:41.280 --> 00:51:44.880
This Divine power can transform you completely

00:51:45.080 --> 00:51:46.760
to such an extent

00:51:46.960 --> 00:51:48.840
that anything that you want to do,

00:51:49.040 --> 00:51:50.800
you can do it in two, three months.

00:51:52.760 --> 00:51:54.920
In Pune when they were singing

00:51:55.400 --> 00:51:58.000
'foreigners' as we call them with respect.

00:51:58.200 --> 00:52:01.440
In India 'foreigners' means respect , not like other countries.

00:52:02.840 --> 00:52:04.040
So they were singing.

00:52:04.240 --> 00:52:07.920
They were some very great musicians (who) had come.

00:52:08.560 --> 00:52:11.880
They told  Me,"Mother, we put down our head to them."

00:52:12.280 --> 00:52:14.120
Because how could these people

00:52:14.320 --> 00:52:18.720
who don't know a word about Indian music have learnt it so well

00:52:18.840 --> 00:52:22.200
and the pronunciation of these Marathi languages were difficult.

00:52:22.400 --> 00:52:24.320
But they are so good at it

00:52:24.520 --> 00:52:26.160
is very surprising.

00:52:27.840 --> 00:52:31.720
Now all this has happened in your presence,

00:52:33.160 --> 00:52:34.280
in your presence.

00:52:35.600 --> 00:52:38.247
It is nice here, you have balloons here.

00:52:38.480 --> 00:52:40.440
to celebrate Christ's birthday.

00:52:40.560 --> 00:52:43.840
and all these balloons of your ego should be burst,

00:52:44.440 --> 00:52:45.560
should be finished.

